==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Moolley
<hw>Mool"ley</hw> }</mhw>,
<pos>a.</pos> <def>Destitute of horns, although belonging to a species
of animals most of which have horns; hornless; polled; <as>as,
<ex>mulley</ex> cattle; a <ex>mulley</ex> (or <ex>moolley</ex>)
cow.</as></def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>muley</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

